story_teamaquamagma_02_03000/2401_1001_0:
If you stand in my way, you’re gonna
get squashed!
Now, now. Both of you, calm down!
I’ve had enough of this! Cut it out, you two!
story_teamaquamagma_02_03000/2401_1001_1: Not until I squash Team Magma!

Until the target...is eliminated...
Can’t...obey orders!
Even that dragon Pokémon is losing ground!
Ugh... Their power keeps on growing...

This isn’t over yet! If all of us work together,
there's always a way!
Don’t forget that we’re here as well, Zinnia!
If you’re ever in trouble, you can count on us!
You guys are gonna make me cry.
Well then... I’ll be needing help from all of you!
story_teamaquamagma_02_03000/2401_1001_2:
Does letting these kids clean up after our mess
look like justice to you?

Absolutely not. We must take responsibility for
our own actions.

Heh, it’s been a while since we’ve had the same
opinion on something.
All right! Let’s get it started!

Or do you need my fist to knock some sense into
that head of yours?!
story_teamaquamagma_02_03000/2401_1001_3:
Paperwork is only the minimum punishment for
repeatedly disobeying orders!
I’m sorry, bro... I can’t stop it anymore...

If I’ve pushed you to that point, then I’ve failed as
a leader...
story_teamaquamagma_02_03000/2401_1001_4:
Hit me with everything you’ve been feeling and
bottling up until now!

It’s my job to deal with my subordinate’s
misdoings.

Courtney! Allow me to share the burden of
your suffering!
